Package boardrelated

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Auctionable
    Auctionable interface is provided to allow the use of auctions in subclasses which have different attributes in auctions.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    birthdayGiftSquare
    birthdayGiftSquare class is provided to meet the needs of the Birthday gift square type.
    Board
    This class mainly acts as a main abstract type keep different types of squares on it.
    bonusSquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the Bonus square type.
    buyableSquare
    This class as the sub-type of Squares allows us progress in a manner that the users can buy, sell, mortgage and build constructions on squares.
    cabSquare
    This class as the sub-type of buyableSquares allows us progress in a manner that the users can buy cab squares and in addition to that build some stands.
    deedSquare
    This class as the sub-type of buyableSquares allows us progress in a manner that the users can buy deed squares and in addition to that build some houses, hotels and skyscrapers on.
    drawCardSquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the squares on which players need to draw cards.
    go2jailSquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the Go To Jail square type.
    goSquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the Go square type.
    hollandTunnelSquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the Holland Tunnel square type.
    incomeTaxSquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the income tax square type.
    luxuryTaxSquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the luxury tax square type.
    paydaySquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the "Payday Play".
    RailroadTrackSquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the railroads.
    reverseDirectionSquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of reverse playing.
    rollOneSquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the play type called "Roll Once Play".
    Square
    This class provides the most methods that are used for the Data Type.
    squezzePlaySquare
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the play type called "Squeeze Play".
    Stock
    This class is provided to meet the needs of the StockMarket.
    StockExchangeSquare
    This class, like any other boardrelated classes, is designed to meet the behaviours of the StockExchangeSquares have.
    StockMarket
    This class is implemented to meet the needs of the stock market.
    taxRefundSquare
    This class is implemented to meet the needs of the tax collection square.
    utilitySquare
    Utility Squares, as data types, have different arrival procedures than any other buyable properties.
